{"word":"H4294 - מַטֶּה - maṭṭeh - mat-teh' - Rod","slug":"H4294","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">מַטֶּה</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>maṭṭeh"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>mat-teh'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Rod"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x05DE;&#x05D8;&#x05BC;&#x05D4;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&#x05DE;&#x05D8;&#x05BC;&#x05D4; - mat&#x0323;t&#x0323;eh  mat&#x0323;t&#x0323;a&#x0302;h</b> - <i>mat-teh', mat-taw'</i><p/>From <a href=\"#/H5186\">H5186</a>; a <i>branch</i> (as <i>extending</i>); figuratively a <i>tribe</i>; also a <i>rod</i>, whether for chastising (figuratively <i>correction</i>), ruling (a <i>sceptre</i>), throwing (a <i>lance</i>), or walking (a <i>staff</i>; figuratively a <i>support</i> of life, for example bread): - rod, staff, tribe."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H3194\">H3194</a>, <a href=\"#/H4295\">H4295</a>, <a href=\"#/H4296\">H4296</a>, <a href=\"#/H4297\">H4297</a>, <a href=\"#/H4298\">H4298</a>, <a href=\"#/H5186\">H5186</a>"}]}